        bStats receives an IP address with each data transmission for
        rate-limiting and abuse prevention.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Retention</strong>: IP addresses are stored for up to
        <strong>60 minutes</strong> solely to track request volume, then
        discarded. They are never linked to accounts or personal profiles.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Legal Basis</strong>: Our legitimate interest in ensuring stable
        service, preventing spam/abuse, and securing our infrastructure.
      </li>
